        "subject": "LU-6242 utils: avoid gcc build errors for liblustreapi_util.c",
        "message": "LU-6242 utils: avoid gcc build errors for liblustreapi_util.c\n\nIf the flag warn-unused-results is set for gcc then\nliblustre_util.c will fail to build due to the return\nvalue of read() being ignored.\n\nChange-Id: Id93da79627180ec9df4baf73e5cacb11a6628297\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@gmail.com>\n"
      },
